{"id": "1456775325387198516", "channel_id": "1451973844872200202", "type": 0, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@1131790839291596841> 觀戰時發現「愈」的誤字還出現在光之子的「聖癒」，同時不確定「侵食」是否本意是想表達「侵蝕」。\n\n另外，敵方對手牌添加侵蝕時，會對牌堆中所有的「幻覺」也加上侵蝕的效果，導致卡面敘述變成「無法打出」隨即接「打出後」，讀起來有點疑惑，感覺真的很幻覺就是了XDDD", "timestamp": "2026-01-02T22:25:03.149000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Alva_goodjob", "emoji_id": "1468259169965707398", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1456775318185578732", "filename": "IMG_2034.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1576445, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451973844872200202/1456775318185578732/IMG_2034.png?ex=69cba0fd&is=69ca4f7d&hm=f2069c93759133916735780eebfa7c89594916aad4b1e703be92e9de1c66e550&"}, {"id": "1456775324409790595", "filename": "IMG_2035.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1547814, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451973844872200202/1456775324409790595/IMG_2035.png?ex=69cba0fe&is=69ca4f7e&hm=12a5603c79be33609f3360df04b0ff249a131de31ac86eef5aa82a771da4d2f0&"}, {"id": "1456775325357707345", "filename": "IMG_2036.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1598385, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451973844872200202/1456775325357707345/IMG_2036.png?ex=69cba0ff&is=69ca4f7f&hm=5f71c1366824ed60fbbe55abd776de90fdd3b08930102983acf6129755b93976&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451973844872200202", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「处理中」常見簡轉繁漏洞：「輓」歌、療「癒」", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1456779016936755493", "channel_id": "1451973844872200202", "type": 0, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "還有一件事 這次觀戰發現很多人第一回合就會打進第二階段，導致播放二階段劇情：「於麗埃特對門內的事物幻滅」，但是第二回合仍然會播放原本預定的劇情「於麗埃特崇敬門內的存有」，使得前後矛盾且解釋不通。如果是重複挑戰的玩家觸發這個狀況，不會有太大問題；但由於茉夏有一回合一條血的能力，現在首次通關普通模式的玩家也會看到演出變長這個樣子。是否考慮微調演出的觸發機制呢👀？\n\n類似的演出順序不正確的狀況也發生在銀芯通訊器，不清楚通訊的觸發條件是什麼，但我曾經發生過先觸發了凱刻斯還錢，才觸發凱刻斯借錢，導致看不懂的狀況。事後通訊的排序有的有變得一照劇情先後，但有的還是看不懂⋯⋯👀", "timestamp": "2026-01-02T22:39:43.283000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-02T22:44:03.363000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Alva_goodjob", "emoji_id": "1468259169965707398", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1456779013375787259", "filename": "IMG_2037.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1593262, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451973844872200202/1456779013375787259/IMG_2037.png?ex=69cba46e&is=69ca52ee&hm=e72dde59a9bb7bac3547db14ab840392153bf4a799b92d4eb82e899a923fea81&"}, {"id": "1456779014009258036", "filename": "IMG_2038.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 831016, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451973844872200202/1456779014009258036/IMG_2038.png?ex=69cba46e&is=69ca52ee&hm=b56f8f0b41fb09b2b46b2ded2d42bd91977b1e55b615cac6e23ff1ca59ecd828&"}, {"id": "1456779014810112164", "filename": "IMG_2039.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 790631, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451973844872200202/1456779014810112164/IMG_2039.png?ex=69cba46e&is=69ca52ee&hm=2b284ee6ec3ff7be63cc76d2a6736c04bc7aa90b59f9ec07cdc897b917ae2d41&"}, {"id": "1456779015431127207", "filename": "IMG_2040.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1323131, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451973844872200202/1456779015431127207/IMG_2040.png?ex=69cba46e&is=69ca52ee&hm=aa6c4df72b783c945c3f5ff6834a967b3dd0ebef5a4c756b347aa97f987396ed&"}, {"id": "1456779016420724971", "filename": "IMG_2041.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1156631, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451973844872200202/1456779016420724971/IMG_2041.png?ex=69cba46f&is=69ca52ef&hm=d4c1f72a262726164785bc76f62455bb121f57c3cd84d0568863b38d843ef134&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451973844872200202", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「处理中」常見簡轉繁漏洞：「輓」歌、療「癒」", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1456511232990249033", "channel_id": "1456511232990249033", "type": 0, "author_id": "1222582796816744458", "author_name": "zhaoxing233", "author_bot": false, "content": "现在的新角色都会伴随专属钥令一起登场，许多专属钥令会影响角色的玩法。但是专属钥令要在主线、个人剧情中等待一周左右的时间来解锁，玩家在抽取新角色后不能马上得到完整的体验<:A_pinch:1432980538536493057> \n希望能够增加一个机制，让角色的专属钥令在角色up时可以暂时解锁（类似繁衍狂热在羊妈活动期间不需要10级好感），通关个人剧情/主线后再正式钥令归档<:dishes:1356083313063759922>", "timestamp": "2026-01-02T04:55:38.615000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1456511232990249033", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "希望活动钥令可以提前解锁", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1456490118683558071", "channel_id": "1456306287884112096", "type": 0, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi, I’ve suggested this in another thread https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1449751537512353863 and mentioned other games which have this function such as Resonance and 異象回聲 (I can’t find its English name but it’s a Chinese game too, both of them are Chinese game). Goya hasn’t replied in text but as the tag has been changed by her, I think BIAV has acknowledged this suggestion. Hopefully they will apply, and if so, in near future.", "timestamp": "2026-01-02T03:31:44.572000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-02T18:27:43.496000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "like", "emoji_id": "1400771686965444648", "count": 3}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Cheerup", "emoji_id": "1400771555939844149", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1456306287884112096", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Options to turn off Enlihtens", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1456706337151914097", "channel_id": "1456306287884112096", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "This would help so much with testing the game and really understanding the complex units, i really hope they will consider it in the future.", "timestamp": "2026-01-02T17:50:55.072000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-02T17:51:05.530000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1456306287884112096", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Options to turn off Enlihtens", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1456735281343365212", "channel_id": "1456306287884112096", "type": 0, "author_id": "595414429957619725", "author_name": "dracozion", "author_bot": false, "content": "Horla is definitely the biggest offender of this but there are also other units who have E's that can be minorly annoying like helots e1 placing an irregular form into hand, or aigis e3 putting a small wish from discard into hand which can cause issues for teams with very little handspace and Thais, or Jenkins e2 causing her def to discard cards unless they are hers. \n\nAdditionally, as V said, this would be very helpful for testing purposes as it is impossible to un-OE or un-enlighten a character to asses their performance and usefulness at various investments or even test their kit. Ie are the enlighten of tawils cards pulled from her ult related to her enlighten level or always assumed to be an e3 copy of the card in the case of something like colorless spiral gaining 20% embryo fusion. \n\nThis also could enable a challenege community to emerge focused around low enlightenment clears as Morimens caters players who enjoy dificult content.", "timestamp": "2026-01-02T19:45:55.905000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-02T19:55:13.169000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1456306287884112096", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Options to turn off Enlihtens", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
